706859f-a.title: Brooklyn: Stanwix Street - Melrose Street
706859f-a.text:
Stanwix Street, east side, north from Melrose Street, shewing in the background, a 9-story building a part of Lpebman Breweries Ino., between Forest and Noll Streets.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
